	/* === appended by tools/apply_translations.cjs === */
	"use with rifle": "配合紫藤之枪使用",
	"Shinobu says a steady supply of bullets would help the slayers": "胡蝶忍说——若紫藤弹源源不绝，便能助队员一臂之力。",
	"black powder and bullets, like the old days.": "炎硝与紫藤弹齐备——一如当年。",
	"the soldier steps out from between the buildings, rifle raised.": "一名守备士兵自屋舍之间走出——紫藤之枪高举。",
	"soldiers patrol the perimeter, rifles slung over their shoulders.": "守备士兵在外围巡逻——紫藤之枪斜挂肩头。",
	"bind kunai blueprint": "缚式苦无・图纸",
	"concentration pill blueprint": "全集中丸・图纸",
