	"永久增益：搭起小屋后自动化解锁。左侧「自动：开/关」按钮可让村民自动伐木/查陷阱。": "永久增益：搭起小屋后自动化解锁。左侧「自动：开/关」按钮可让村民自动伐木/查陷阱。",
	"Demon Raid": "鬼夜袭",
	"the watch crow caws frantically before dawn.": "黎明之前，望哨鸦发出急促的鸣叫。",
	"three lesser demons have torn through the outer fence and reached the storehouses.": "三只低级鬼撕开了外围栅栏，已经摸到了仓房一侧。",
	"villagers scatter. the slayers grab whatever blade is nearest.": "村民四散奔逃。队员们抓起手边任何一把刀刃。",
	"lesser demons breach the wisteria gate.": "低级鬼破开紫藤外门。",
	"rally the slayers": "召集队员迎战",
	"seal the inner gate": "封闭内门",
	"the slayers cut the demons down before sunlight finishes the work.": "队员先一步斩翻了来犯之鬼——剩下的留给了即将升起的朝阳。",
	"a few villagers are wounded but none have turned.": "几名村民受了伤，但无人鬼化。",
	"Shinobu collects samples from the ash for her medicine cabinet.": "胡蝶忍从灰烬里取了样品，收进她的药匣。",
	"the raid is repelled. medicine stocks improve.": "袭击被击退，药品储备增加。",
	"clean the courtyard": "清扫庭院",
	"the slayers are inexperienced. two are bitten before the demons fall.": "队员尚不老练。鬼倒下之前，两人被咬伤。",
	"Shinobu drags them inside and works through the night.": "胡蝶忍将伤者拖入屋内，连夜医治。",
	"the bitten are saved, but the food stores were trampled in the fight.": "被咬之人保住了，但仓房里的食物在乱战中被踏毁了大半。",
	"the raid is repelled, at a cost.": "袭击虽被击退——代价并不轻。",
	"count the dead": "清点亡者",
	"the inner gate holds. the outer ring does not.": "内门守住了。外围则没有。",
	"by dawn the demons have fled, leaving silence and the scent of iron.": "黎明时分，鬼已退去——只留下死寂与铁锈的气味。",
	"several villagers were outside the wall when the alarm sounded.": "警讯响起之时，仍有数名村民困在墙外。",
	"the wisteria gate holds. the outer ring does not.": "紫藤之门守住了。外围则没有。",
	"mourn the lost": "为亡者默哀",
	"A Creeping Sickness": "蔓延之症",
	"Shinobu finds black specks in three villagers' blood under the lamp.": "胡蝶忍在油灯下检查三名村民的血——里面浮着细小黑点。",
	"it is not a demon turning, she says. it is something the demons left behind in the well.": "她说，这不是鬼化的前兆——而是鬼留在井水里的某种东西。",
	"she can stop it, but she will need a great deal of medicine 窶・and quickly.": "她说她能止住它——但需要大量药品，且要快。",
	"a sickness spreads through the village.": "村庄之中疫病渐起。",
	"hand over the medicine": "悉数交出药品",
	"ration the medicine 窶・save half for emergencies": "克扣一半，留作应急",
	"leave it to nature": "听天由命",
	"Shinobu works without sleep for three days. all sick villagers recover.": "胡蝶忍三日不眠——所有染疾的村民最终痊愈。",
	"she leaves a flask of distilled wisteria oil on your desk in thanks.": "她在你的桌上留下一瓶亲手蒸馏的紫藤油，作为答谢。",
	"the sickness passes. Shinobu shares her work.": "疫病退去。胡蝶忍分享了她的成果。",
	"let her rest": "让她去歇息",
	"the medicine reaches the sick in time. most recover.": "药品及时送到——多数人康复。",
	"a handful never wake. the rest of the village goes on.": "少数人再未醒来。村庄继续运转。",
	"the sickness passes 窶・barely.": "疫病堪堪退去。",
	"bury the dead": "安葬亡者",
	"the rationed medicine was not enough. by the time more was sent, the sick were past saving.": "克扣后的药量远远不够——再添时，染疾者已无可救。",
	"the surviving villagers withdraw deeper into the estate.": "幸存者退向庄园深处。",
	"the sickness takes its share.": "疫病取走了它的那一份。",
	"see to the survivors": "看顾幸存者",
	"within a week the well is condemned. within two, the lodge is a hospice.": "一周之内，水井已成禁地。两周之后，猎屋成了临时病坊。",
	"Shinobu does what she can with field herbs. it is not enough.": "胡蝶忍用田间野草尽力一试——杯水车薪。",
	"the sickness eats deep into the village.": "疫病深深咬入村庄。",
	"regret it": "为此追悔",
	"Tainted Water": "污浊之水",
	"the upstream brook runs red at first light.": "破晓时分，上游溪流泛起一抹暗红。",
	"a slayer rides in: a demon was killed two ridges over, and the river carried the rot here.": "一名队员策马而至——两座山外斩杀了一只鬼，腐血随河水流至此地。",
	"the smokehouse meat that drank that water cannot be saved.": "用过那水的熏房之肉，已无可救。",
	"a demon carcass has tainted the water upstream.": "一具鬼尸污染了上游水脉。",
	"burn the tainted meat": "焚毁污肉",
	"try to distill it (consumes wood)": "尝试蒸馏（耗木材）",
	"the smokehouse goes up in a thick column of greasy smoke.": "熏房腾起一柱浓黑油烟。",
	"the village will be hungry for a week, but no one will turn.": "村庄将饥饿一周——但无人鬼化。",
	"the tainted meat is burned. the river clears in days.": "污肉焚尽。河水数日后清澈如初。",
	"walk away from the smoke": "走出烟雾",
	"the wood-fire distillation works. clean water, clean meat.": "柴火蒸馏奏效——水净、肉净。",
	"Shinobu salts what is left and stores it again.": "胡蝶忍把剩下的肉重新腌渍，封入新缸。",
	"the meat is saved.": "肉得以保全。",
	"thank Shinobu": "向胡蝶忍致谢",
	"the distillation works for most of the smokehouse 窶・about half is still ruined.": "蒸馏只保住了一半熏房——另一半仍要丢弃。",
	"no one falls sick, but the storage is thin.": "无人染疾——但储备已显得单薄。",
	"half the meat is saved.": "一半的肉得以保全。",
	"be grateful": "心怀感激",

