	"the sounds fade into the wind. you gather a few sticks on the way back.": "声响渐没于风中。归途上你顺手拾起几根柴枝。",

	/* === appended by tools/apply_translations.cjs === */
	"the crow is found at dawn 窶・broken on the wall, the writ shredded in its talons.": "破晓时分，传讯鸦被发现倒毙于墙下——爪中令印已被撕成碎片。",
	"whatever provisions the Corps sent were scattered in the night. only scraps remain.": "鬼杀队遣送之物在夜里被洒落殆尽——只余零星碎屑。",
	"this hunt, you go alone.": "这一回任务——你只能孤身前往。",
	"the rider crow falls 窶・most of the provisions are lost.": "支援任务失败——绝大多数补给散失。",
	"prepare to depart anyway": "无论如何，整装出发",
	"a hand of fingers too long reaches from behind the woodpile.": "一只指节过长的手——从柴堆后伸出。",
	"you twist away 窶・but not before claws find skin. the demon vanishes into the dark.": "你旋身闪避——但爪尖仍触及肌肤。鬼影旋即没入黑暗。",
	"the wound burns. you stagger inside, leaving a trail.": "伤口灼热作痛。你跌撞回屋，留下一道血痕。",
	"a demon strikes from the woodpile 窶・you take wounds.": "柴堆中冲出一鬼——你身负伤痕。",
	"limp back inside": "踉跄返回屋内",

